{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03249/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03249"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:32:49"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["eye-level"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, tracking, crane, tilt"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man and woman walk through a restaurant."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03249","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03249"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1/abe82d0e-8edd-47cd-b7ee-63d8d6fbc7d2","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:02:29.671Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The gown that Reynolds dresses Alma in at first is very similar to her waitress outfit. Likewise, the dress <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW235834751 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04303.html\"><u>she wears during the fashion show</u></a> at the House of Woodcock is a more developed version of her waitress outfit, too. He accentuates her beauty but also keeps her in this subservient role.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:270.2912621359223,513.5922330097087,515.7281553398059,428.7378640776699"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1/8aa69ef3-7fa9-4971-9f89-e72d63c2e38c","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T14:02:44.451Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In a room filled largely with men in tuxedoes, Alma stands out even more with her colorful dress. She brings something new to Reynolds’s life.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03249/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1516.116504854369,352.0388349514563,365.04854368932047,354.17475728155335"}}}]}]}]}